(2.2 European Union - MDR 2017/745, Annex VIII, Rule 11) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(    DermaRash is not software intended to provide information which is) Tj
T*
(    used to take decisions with diagnosis or therapeutic purposes. It) Tj
T*
(    provides general educational information only. It does not qualify) Tj
T*
(    as a medical device under Article 2\(1\) and is therefore outside the) Tj
T*
(    scope of MDR 2017/745.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2.3 United Kingdom - MHRA "Software and AI as a Medical Device") Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(    DermaRash does not meet the functional definition of a Software as a) Tj
T*
(    Medical Device \(SaMD\) under the MHRA guidance because its output is) Tj
T*
